headline: Visa Stock Hits Buy Point Amid This Surprising Consumer Trend
summary: Shares of Visa have been rising since the company beat quarterly estimates last week.  Visa stock made a solid move back above its 50-day moving average April 30, the day after it reported sales and earnings that topped analyst expectations.  The company also set a $30 billion stock buyback program.
